@ScrumMaster.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5104

### Submit a standup entry
POST {{ScrumMaster.API_HostAddress}}/standup/submit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "memberName": "John Doe",
  "yesterday": "Reviewed pull requests and fixed login bug",
  "today": "Implement user profile API endpoint",
  "blockers": ""
}

###

### Get all submissions
GET {{ScrumMaster.API_HostAddress}}/standup/submissions
Accept: application/json

###

### Analyze standup submissions
POST {{ScrumMaster.API_HostAddress}}/standup/analyze
Accept: application/json

###

### Clear all submissions
DELETE {{ScrumMaster.API_HostAddress}}/standup/submissions
Accept: application/json

###
